data.description: 5331 Wishing Arch - Your Dream Waterfront Home Awaits!  Welcome to this magnificent property in the Amazing Mirabay community of Apollo Beach, Florida. Situated at 5331 Wishing Arch, this remarkable home offers everything you've been dreaming of for your waterfront lifestyle.  Prime Location: Nestled on the lagoon in Mirabay, this home provides direct access to Tampa Bay from your back door within minutes.   Dockable Lot: This property has been prepermitted for a dock and has obtained the necessary easement, County and HOA approvals!  Outdoor Paradise: The spacious yard offers ample room for a large pool and the summer kitchen is pre plumbed, creating the perfect outdoor oasis for relaxation and entertainment.  Luxurious Features: Step inside to discover the extensive high-end touches throughout, including captivating feature walls, intricately carved stair rails, and exquisite light fixtures.  Open and Bright: Beautiful large windows and full wall glass sliders plus light low maintenance floors adorn the first floor, creating a bright and open atmosphere.  Gourmet Kitchen: The upgraded kitchen boasts stunning Quartz countertops, a generous island, and a sunny open eating area.   Master Suite: The huge first-floor master suite is your private retreat, complete with a walk-in closet, ensuite bath featuring double sinks, and an oversized rainhead double shower.  Additional Primary Suite: Don't forget, there's a second primary bedroom with an ensuite bath on the second floor, perfect for accommodating guests or family members.  Additional Living Space: Upstairs, you'll find three more bedrooms and a roomy loft, ideal for creating an additional living area or home office.  Better Than New: Built in 2021 and meticulously updated, this home is better than new, ensuring a modern and effortless living experience.  360-Degree Views: It's the Largo floorplan by Park Square Homes and sits at the top of the developments peninsula, offering the largest 360 views of the beautiful Mirabay Lagoon.  Unrestricted Access: You can boat to Tampa Bay right from your backyard with unrestricted access.  Property Specs: With 4 beds, 3.5 baths, and a spacious 2,922 square feet, this home is designed for both comfort and luxury. Check out the oversized 3 car garage just waiting for your vehicles, bikes, kayaks and golf cart!  Community Perks:  Mirabay offers an array of amenities, including  2 resort-style heated pools, 24 hour fitness center, tennis courts, basketball, pickleball, kayaking, multiple parks and its very own shopping and dining village.  5331 Wishing Arch is not just a property; it's a gateway to a waterfront lifestyle filled with adventure and relaxation. Whether you're a boating enthusiast, a lover of outdoor living, or someone who appreciates fine craftsmanship, this home has it all.    Don't miss your chance to own this piece of paradise. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and make this dream waterfront home your own!
